org.anyframe.scheduling
Class TriggerInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.anyframe.scheduling.TriggerInfo

public class TriggerInfo
extends Object

This TriggerInfo class contains attributes for spring scheduling trigger bean information and getter, setter methods of them. And it contains toString method for logging.

Author:
